Package: toth
Title: Reproducible Analytics Framework with DVC and Docker Integration
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sebastian", "Rauschert", , "seb.rauschert@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive framework for setting up reproducible analytics projects
    with integrated version control for data (DVC), containerization (Docker),
    dependency management (renv), and customizable reporting (Quarto).
    Provides tools and templates for best-practice project organization and workflow management.
